A4">Michael Moïssey Postan; Edward Miller (1987). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=cHRvtwTLcMAC&amp;pg=PA417" id="mwCA8"><i id="mwCBA">The Cambridge Economic History of Europe: Trade and industry in the Middle Ages</i></a>. Cambridge University Press. pp.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwCBE"> </span>417–. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwCBI">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwCBM"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-0-521-08709-4" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-521-08709-4" id="mwCBQ">978-0-521-08709-4</a><span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwCBU">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwCBY">May 31,</span> 2012</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Cambridge+Economic+History+of+Europe%3A+Trade+and+industry+in+the+Middle+Ages&amp;rft.pages=417-&amp;rft.pub=Cambridge+University+Press&amp;rft.date=1987&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-521-08709-4&amp;rft.au=Michael+Mo%C3%AFssey+Postan&amp;rft.au=Edward+Miller&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DcHRvtwTLcMAC%26pg%3DPA417&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASlavery" class="Z3988" about="#mwt269" id="mwCBc"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt269" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwCBg"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-82" id="cite_note-82"><a href="./Slavery#cite_ref-82" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-82" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt270" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"firs