ry#cite_ref-114" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-114" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation news" about="#mwt377" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite news","href":"./Template:Cite_news"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/1523100.stm"},"title":{"wt":"Focus on the slave trade"},"publisher":{"wt":"BBC"},"date":{"wt":"3 September 2001"},"archive-url":{"wt":"https://web.archive.org/web/20170525101036/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/1523100.stm"},"archive-date":{"wt":"25 May 2017"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCPU"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20170525101036/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/1523100.stm" id="mwCPY">"Focus on the slave trade"</a>. BBC. 3 September 2001. Archived from <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/1523100.stm" id="mwCPc">the original</a> on 25 May 2017.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Focus+on+the+slave+trade&amp;rft.date=2001-09-03&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.bbc.co.uk%2F2%2Fhi%2Fafrica%2F1523100.stm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASlavery" class="Z3988" about="#mwt377" id="mwCPg"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt377" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwCPk"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-115" id="cite_note-115"><a href="./Slavery#cite_ref-115" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-115" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt414" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book","href":"./Template:Cite_book"}