CXM"><i id="mwCXQ">Case Studies on Human Rights And Fundamental Freedoms: A World Survey</i></a>. Martinus Nijhoff Publishers. pp.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwCXU"> </span>440–. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwCXY">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwCXc"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-90-247-1956-3" title="Special:BookSources/978-90-247-1956-3" id="mwCXg">978-90-247-1956-3</a><span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwCXk">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwCXo">May 31,</span> 2012</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Case+Studies+on+Human+Rights+And+Fundamental+Freedoms%3A+A+World+Survey&amp;rft.pages=440-&amp;rft.pub=Martinus+Nijhoff+Publishers&amp;rft.date=1977&amp;rft.isbn=978-90-247-1956-3&amp;rft.au=Willem+A.+Veenhoven&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D0lSH6-0HRaYC%26pg%3DPA440&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASlavery" class="Z3988" about="#mwt468" id="mwCXs"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt468" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwCXw"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-Snell-139" id="cite_note-Snell-139"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Slavery#cite_ref-Snell_139-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Slavery#cite_ref-Snell_139-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-Snell-139" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt481" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"last":{"wt":"Snell"},"first":{"wt":"Daniel C."},"title":{"wt":"The Cambridge World History o