lavery#cite_ref-207" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-207" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt1076" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite web","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"http://www.christianitytoday.com/history/issues/issue-33/why-christians-supported-slavery.html#storystream"},"title":{"wt":"Why Did So Many Christians Support Slavery?"},"website":{"wt":"christianitytoday.com"},"accessdate":{"wt":"August 28, 2017"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCvk"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.christianitytoday.com/history/issues/issue-33/why-christians-supported-slavery.html#storystream" id="mwCvo">"Why Did So Many Christians Support Slavery?"</a>. <i id="mwCvs">christianitytoday.com</i><span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwCvw">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwCv0">August 28,</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=christianitytoday.com&amp;rft.atitle=Why+Did+So+Many+Christians+Support+Slavery%3F&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.christianitytoday.com%2Fhistory%2Fissues%2Fissue-33%2Fwhy-christians-supported-slavery.html%23storystream&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASlavery" class="Z3988" about="#mwt1076" id="mwCv4"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt1076" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwCv8"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-208" id="cite_note-208"><a href="./Slavery#cite_ref-208" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-208" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.civil-war.net/pages/1860_census.html" id="mwCwA">1860 Census Results</a> <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20040604075834/http://www.civil-war.net/pages/1860_census.html" about="#mwt1079" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"webarchive","href":"./Template:Webarchive"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"https://web.archive.org/web/20040604075834/http://www.civil-war.net/pages/1860_census.html"},"date":{"wt":"June 4, 2004"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCwE">Archived</a><span about="#mwt1079" id="mwCwI"> June 4, 2004, at the </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Wayback_Machine" title="Wayback Machine" about="#mwt1079" id="mwCwM">Wayback Machine</a><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Webarchive_template_wayback_links" about="#mwt1079" id="mwCwQ"/>, The Civil War Home Page.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-209" id="cite_note-209"><a href="./Slavery#cite_ref-209" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-209" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt1080" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite web","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"https://www.theatlantic.com/national/archive/2010/08/small-truth-papering-over-a-big-lie/61136/"},"title":{"wt":"Small Truth Papering Over a Big Lie"},"publisher":{"wt":"The Atlantic"},"date":{"wt":"August 9, 2010"},"accessdate":{"wt":"September 29, 2015"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCwU"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://www.theatlantic.com/national/archive/2010/08/small-truth-papering-over-a-big-lie/61136/" id="mwCwY">"Small Truth Papering Over a Big Lie"</a>. The Atlantic. August 9, 2010<span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwCwc">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwCwg">September 29,</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Small+Truth