ravos: O Comércio Luso-Brasileiro do Álcool em Mpinda, Luanda e Benguela durante o Tráfico Atlântico de Escravos (c. 1480–1830) e o Seu Impacto nas Sociedades da África Central Ocidental</a>. Translated by Márcia Lameirinhas. Tempos e Espaços Africanos Series, vol. 3. Lisbon: Editora Vulgata, 2002. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt1863" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"978-972-8427-24-5"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwDmY"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" about="#mwt1863" id="mwDmc">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt1863" id="mwDmg"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-972-8427-24-5" title="Special:BookSources/978-972-8427-24-5" about="#mwt1863" id="mwDmk">978-972-8427-24-5</a>.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-apology-335" id="cite_note-apology-335"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Slavery#cite_ref-apology_335-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Slavery#cite_ref-apology_335-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-apology-335" class="mw-reference-text">"<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2010/04/23/opinion/23gates.html?pagewanted=all&amp;_r=0" id="mwDmo">Ending the Slavery Blame-Game</a>", <i id="mwDms">The New York Times</i>. April 22, 2010.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-dahomey-336" id="cite_note-dahomey-336"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Slavery#cite_ref-dahomey_336-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Slavery#cite_ref-dahomey_336-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-dahomey-336" class="mw-reference-text">"<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://articles.chicagotribune.co