</section><section data-mw-section-id="67" id="mwDvk"><h2 id="Bibliography_and_further_reading">Bibliography and further reading</h2>

<section data-mw-section-id="68" id="mwDvo"><h3 id="Surveys_and_reference">Surveys and reference</h3>
<ul id="mwDvs"><li id="mwDvw"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt2042" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"first":{"wt":"Kevin"},"last":{"wt":"Bales"},"title":{"wt":"Disposable People: New Slavery in the Global Economy"},"url":{"wt":"{{google books |plainurl=y |id=djQq6-pZqNcC}}"},"year":{"wt":"1999"},"publisher":{"wt":"University of California Press"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-0-520-21797-3"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwDv0">Bales, Kevin (1999). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=djQq6-pZqNcC"><i>Disposable People: New Slavery in the Global Economy</i></a>. University of California Press. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-0-520-21797-3" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-520-21797-3">978-0-520-21797-3</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Disposable+People%3A+New+Slavery+in+the+Global+Economy&amp;rft.pub=University+of+California+Press&amp;rft.date=1999&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-520-21797-3&amp;rft.aulast=Bales&amp;rft.aufirst=Kevin&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DdjQq6-pZqNcC&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASlavery" class="Z3988" about="#mwt2042"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt2042" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}'/></li>
