<dl id="mwD1U"><dt id="mwD1Y">Slavery in the modern era</dt></dl>
<ul id="mwD1c"><li id="mwD1g"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt2529" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"first":{"wt":"Jesse"},"last":{"wt":"Sage"},"title":{"wt":"Enslaved: True Stories of Modern Day Slavery"},"url":{"wt":"{{google books |plainurl=y |id=RwtfBwAAQBAJ}}"},"year":{"wt":"2015"},"publisher":{"wt":"St. Martin&apos;s Press"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-1-250-08310-4"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwD1k">Sage, Jesse (2015). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=RwtfBwAAQBAJ"><i>Enslaved: True Stories of Modern Day Slavery</i></a>. St. Martin's Press. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-1-250-08310-4" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-250-08310-4">978-1-250-08310-4</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Enslaved%3A+True+Stories+of+Modern+Day+Slavery&amp;rft.pub=St.+Martin%27s+Press&amp;rft.date=2015&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-250-08310-4&amp;rft.aulast=Sage&amp;rft.aufirst=Jesse&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DRwtfBwAAQBAJ&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASlavery" class="Z3988" about="#mwt2529"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt2529" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}'/></li>
