</section><section data-mw-section-id="71" id="mwD50"><h3 id="Modern">Modern</h3>
<ul id="mwD54"><li id="mwD58"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.youmanity.today/en/latests/the-last-african-slaves.html" id="mwD6A">The Last African Slaves</a></li>
